'''基瓦屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Kiwa'''''}}）是[[十足目|十足目]]之下的一個海洋生物屬，物種全是居住於深海的[[深海熱泉|熱泉]]或[[冷泉|冷泉]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cas.ac.cn/xw/cmsm/201307/t20130726_3905931.shtml |title=冷泉：海底“沙漠中的绿洲”|language=zh-hans|publisher=《[[中國科學報|中國科學報]]》|date=2013-07-26| accessdate=2013-07-30 |page=12 }}</ref>。基瓦屬是'''基瓦科'''（{{lang|la|'''Kiwaidae'''}}）之下的唯一一個屬，屬於[[劣柱蝦總科|劣柱蝦總科]]（{{lang|la|Chirostyloidea}}）<ref name="Schnabel">{{cite journal |author=K. E. Schnabel, S. T. Ahyong & E. W. Maas |year=2011 |title=Galatheoidea are not monophyletic – molecular and morphological phylogeny of the squat lobsters (Decapoda: Anomura) with recognition of a new superfamily |journal=[[Molecular_Phylogenetics_and_Evolution|Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution]] |volume=58 |issue=2 |pages=157–168 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2010.11.011 |pmid=21095236}}</ref>。現時只有兩個物種，分別是2005年發現的[[基瓦多毛怪|基瓦多毛怪]]（{{lang|la|''Kiwa hirsuta''}}）<ref name=qqnews /><ref name=MP>{{cite journal|author=E. Macpherson, W. Jones & M. Segonzac |year=2006 |url=http://www.mnhn.fr/museum/front/medias/publication/6892_z05n4a3.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |title=A new squat lobster family of Galatheoidea (Crustacea, Decapoda, Anomura) from the hydrothermal vents of the Pacific-Antarctic Ridge |journal=[[Zoosystema|Zoosystema]] |volume=27 |issue=4 |pages=709–723 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204062927/http://www.mnhn.fr/museum/front/medias/publication/6892_z05n4a3.pdf |archivedate=2012-02-04 }}</ref>及2006年發現的[[雪人蟹|雪人蟹]]（{{lang|la|''Kiwa puravida''}}）<ref name=ettoday-137840 /><ref name="thurber">{{cite journal |author=Andrew R. Thurber, William J. Jones & Kareen Schnabel |year=2011 |title=Dancing for food in the deep sea: bacterial farming by a new species of yeti crab |journal=[[PLoS_ONE|PLoS ONE]] |volume=6 |issue=11 |page=e26243 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0026243 |url=http://www.plosone.org/article/info%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0026243 |access-date=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104210411/http://www.plosone.org/article/info%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0026243 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。未來還可能有第三個物種，是一種於2009年在[[南極|南極]][[斯科舍板块|斯科舍板块]]上的[[東斯科舍洋脊|東斯科舍洋脊]]發現的[[未命名物種|未命名物種]](Kiwa n. sp.)、暫時被稱為「[[霍夫蟹|霍夫蟹]]」的生物<ref name="thurber" /><ref name="rogers">{{cite journal |author=Alex D. Rogers, Paul A. Tyler, Douglas P. Connelly, Jon T. Copley, Rachael James ''et al.'' |year=2012 |title=The discovery of new deep-sea hydrothermal vent communities in the Southern Ocean and implications for biogeography |journal=[[PLoS_Biology|PLoS Biology]] |volume=10 |issue=1 |page=e1001234 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1001234 |pmid=22235194}}</ref>。這一種「霍夫蟹」得名於[[美國演員|美國演員]][[大衛·赫索霍夫|大衛·赫索霍夫]]，現時根據其[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]及[[細胞核|細胞核]]的[[rDNA|rDNA]]分析，確認這物種在遺傳學上與基瓦多毛怪是不同的物種兩者大約在1200萬年前分開<ref name="rogers" />。2011年，在[[西南印度洋脊|西南印度洋脊]]的[[深海噴泉|深海噴泉]]又發現一種與在東斯科舍洋脊發現的物種非常相似的物種<ref name=bbc>{{cite news |title=Deep-sea creatures at volcanic vent |author=Rebecca Morelle |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |language=en |date=2011-12-28 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16267625 |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2013-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130821095818/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-16267625 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 語源 ==
“基瓦屬”這個名詞源於“基瓦屬”這個名詞源於[[波里尼西亞|波里尼西亞]]傳說的貝殼女神[[基瓦|基瓦]](Kiwa)，儘管[[毛利人|毛利人]]崇拜的男性海神也叫作「基瓦」<ref>{{cite book | author = [[Elsdon_Best|Elsdon Best]] | title = The Maori - Volume 1 | chapter = IV. Cosmogony and Anthropogeny | pages = 89–105 | chapterurl = http://www.nzetc.org/tm/scholarly/tei-Bes01Maor-t1-body-d4.html | year = 1924 | access-date = 2013-07-30 | archive-date = 2012-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204064219/http://www.nzetc.org/tm/scholarly/tei-Bes01Maor-t1-body-d4.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==分類==
基瓦屬的第一個物種[[基瓦多毛怪|基瓦多毛怪]]（{{lang|la|''Kiwa hirsuta''}}）於2005年在[[复活节岛|复活节岛]]以南1500公里的太平洋海底發現之時<ref name=qqnews>{{cite news |url=http://news.qq.com/a/20060318/001165.htm |title=法科学家发现深海怪物 不伦不类种属难定 |date=2006-03-18 |language=zh-hans }}</ref>，无论从[[形态生物学|形态生物学]]还是[[分子生物学|分子生物学]]的角度出发均无法分入任何现存的科或属中，因此暂独自构成同名的[[科|科]]和[[属|属]]<ref name="Macpherson">{{cite journal|author=E. Macpherson, W. Jones & M. Segonzac |year=2006 |url=http://www.mnhn.fr/museum/front/medias/publication/6892_z05n4a3.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |title=A new squat lobster family of Galatheoidea (Crustacea, Decapoda, Anomura) from the hydrothermal vents of the Pacific-Antarctic Ridge |journal=[[Zoosystema|Zoosystema]] |volume=27 |issue=4 |pages=709–723 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204062927/http://www.mnhn.fr/museum/front/medias/publication/6892_z05n4a3.pdf |archivedate=2012-02-04 }}</ref>，直到後來科學家在南極發現一種可歸入同科同屬的新物種[[雪人蟹|雪人蟹]]（{{lang|la|''Kiwa puravida''}}）<ref name=ettoday-137840>{{cite news |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20121210/137840.htm |title=國家地理雜誌「2012十大發現」　從無腳蚓螈到糖太陽：6.南極海底的「雪人蟹」 |date=2012-12-10 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |language=zh-hant |publisher=[[ETToday|ETToday]]新聞雲 |archive-date=2013-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208224158/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20121210/137840.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ettoday-10813>{{cite news |url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20111205/10813.htm |title=潛居深海的「雪人蟹」　在鉗子上種細菌自給自足 |date=2011-12-05 |accessdate=2013-07-06 |language=zh-hant |publisher=[[ETToday|ETToday]]新聞雲 |archive-date=2013-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131228161159/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20111205/10813.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基瓦科最初被歸入[[铠甲虾总科|铠甲虾总科]]，隨後發現[[鎧甲蝦類|鎧甲蝦類]]並非[[單系群|單系群]]，鎧甲蝦總科一分為二，再被歸入[[劣柱蝦總科|劣柱蝦總科]]。

